The evidence with the title 'The Obama Phone? - FactCheck.org ' says Oct 29, 2009  ... Q : has the Obama administration started a program to use "taxpayer money" to give free cell phones to welfare recipients ? A: no.  ... Welfare recipients , and others , can receive a free cell phone, but the program is not funded by the government or taxpayer money , as the e-mail alleges. And it's hardly new. 
